%section.breakdown.white
	.contents
		%h2 What's what in NeverFold

		.row.clearfix

			.col.first
				.figure
					%img{src:"/assets/welcome/breakdown/bamboo.jpg"}
				.title Exotic Wood
				.description
					This sleek piece of caramelized bamboo, poplar and walnut is a sturdy, natural timber that will mesh into your closet well.

			.col
				.figure
					%img{src:"/assets/welcome/breakdown/nonslip.jpg"}
				.title No Slip and Falls
				.description
					Attractive wooden rods are selected to complement the exotic wood. It has silicone-based non-slip surface to prevent your stack from sliding off.

		.row.clearfix{style:"margin-top:40px;"}

			.col.first
				.figure
					%img{src:"/assets/welcome/breakdown/adjustlock.jpg"}
				.title Adjust and Lock
				.description
					Adjust distances between the rods depending on your stack's thickness. Rods snap in place prevent NeverFold from rolling your stash over.

			.col
				.figure
					%img{src:"/assets/welcome/breakdown/usaflag.jpg"}
				.title Made in the USA
				.description
					The bars are hand-cut, sanded, and assembled individually by a skilled woodsman right here in the United States, not from a factory overseas.

